Package: claudeCodeR
Type: Package
Title: Claude Code Integration for RStudio
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Tyler", "Lifke", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides Claude Code AI assistant integration for RStudio via the Claude Agent SDK.
    Includes an interactive Shiny gadget interface for chatting with Claude and applying
    code modifications directly in the RStudio editor. Supports both Anthropic API and
    AWS Bedrock authentication.
